design
------
- singleton wall variants are considerate of their neighbours ...
  - use same colour and style
  - shapes and slopes create sensible larger pieces i.e. no slope with a block above it.

programming
-----------
- pushing might be improved by animating bob and then moving the boulder on 3/4ths of his delta
- collision detection might be improved by looking at deltas to gauge distance
- boulderUpdate flag which triggers 
  - when bob moves a boulder
  - when bob digs earth, diamonds, keys
  - keys open safes
  - spirits enter cages
  - a boulder falls

